          "Gain temporary fire resistance when touching lava\n\nDue to the extreme heat,\nthis doesn't seem to work in the nether.",
          "Enjoy a longer lasting fire resistance when swimming\nin lava that can be used more often than before.\n\nThough it still doesn't seem to work in the nether..."
        ]
